# AI - SENTIMENT ANALYZER


# A cloud-based web application that analyzes text sentiment using VADER Sentiment Analysis with a modern, interactive dashboard.

# âœ¨ Features
# Real-time sentiment analysis (Positive/Negative/Neutral)

# Detailed sentiment breakdown with percentages

# Compound score visualization (-1 to +1 scale)

# Dark/Light mode toggle for better UX

# Responsive design works on all devices

# Easy deployment to Heroku or GitHub Pages

